snippet.title: Amber Heard Loses 20 Lbs From Stress
snippet.description:
Amber Heard has reportedly lost 20 pounds due to stress, as court proceedings with Johnny Depp have been postponed until next month. The Danish Girl actress was scheduled to fly to London for a costume fitting this week, but sources say she never left LA, after producers cancelled the booking, fearing shed dropped too much weight.
Kim Kardashian had claimed that Taylor Swift "approved" of the song 'Famous' by hubby Kanye West where he refers to Taylor as the 'b' word. However, Taylor has denied the claims, saying that the first time she heard it was when the song was first released and that she felt "humiliated".
Dwayne The Rock Johnson hasn't eaten candy since 1989.
That's nearly 30 years since he's eaten a sugary treat.  Jimmy Fallon tried to temp Dwayne to break his ban with an array of candies on The Tonight Show, and The Rock finally caved in!Christina Grimmie has been laid to rest in her home state of New Jersey, one week after her tragic death. The Voice star, who was shot and killed while signing autographs at her concert in Orlando, was remembered during a private funeral with close friends and family. The service was paid for by Christinas mentor on The Voice, Adam Levine, who paid an emotional tribute to her following her tragic death.
